<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Newsletter Example Gallery</title>
  <style>
    :root {
      --bg: #f2efe8;
      --paper: #ffffff;
      --paper-soft: #fbf7f0;
      --text: #1d1a16;
      --muted: #6a655d;
      --line: #d8cec2;
      --accent: #9f3a2f;
      --accent-soft: #f8e3d8;
      --accent-2: #315c7c;
      --shadow: rgba(65, 43, 19, 0.08);
    }

    * { box-sizing: border-box; }

    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: "Source Sans 3", "Segoe UI", "Helvetica Neue", Arial, sans-serif;
      color: var(--text);
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at top left, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9), transparent 30%),
        linear-gradient(180deg, #f7f1e6 0%, var(--bg) 45%, #ede3d6 100%);
    }

    .wrap {
      max-width: 1520px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 24px 20px 36px;
    }

    .hero {
      display: block;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }

    .hero-copy {
      width: min(100%, 1320px);
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 22px 24px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(159, 58, 47, 0.16);
      border-radius: 18px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.94), rgba(251, 247, 240, 0.92));
      box-shadow: 0 14px 32px var(--shadow);
    }

    .eyebrow {
      margin: 0 0 6px;
      color: var(--accent);
      font-size: 0.74rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 0.14em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    h1 {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: "Fraunces", "Iowan Old Style", "Palatino Linotype", Georgia, serif;
      font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 3vw, 2.6rem);
      line-height: 1.04;
      letter-spacing: -0.04em;
    }

    .lead {
      margin: 8px 0 0;
      color: var(--muted);
      max-width: 60rem;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      line-height: 1.55;
    }

    .hero-note {
      margin: 14px 0 0;
      display: inline-flex;
      gap: 8px;
      align-items: center;
      color: var(--accent-2);
      background: rgba(49, 92, 124, 0.08);
      border: 1px solid rgba(49, 92, 124, 0.14);
      border-radius: 999px;
      padding: 7px 12px;
      font-size: 0.86rem;
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    .hero-aside {
      display: none;
    }

    .hero-aside p {
      margin: 0;
      color: var(--muted);
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .hero-aside strong {
      display: block;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
      color: var(--text);
      font-size: 0.95rem;
    }

    .section-head {
      display: flex;
      width: min(100%, 1320px);
      margin: 0 auto 14px;
      align-items: baseline;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 16px;
      padding-bottom: 10px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
    }

    .section-head h2 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.14em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--accent);
    }

    .section-head p {
      margin: 0;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 0.92rem;
    }

    .grid {
      display: grid;
      gap: 22px;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      justify-items: center;
    }

    .card {
      width: min(100%, 1320px);
      background: var(--paper);
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius: 18px;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 12px 28px var(--shadow);
    }

    .card-header {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr) auto;
      gap: 16px;
      padding: 18px 20px 16px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, #fffdf9 0%, #f7f1e7 100%);
    }

    .card-header h2 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      line-height: 1.25;
    }

    .card-header p {
      margin: 6px 0 0;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 0.94rem;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }

    .card-header .actions {
      display: flex;
      align-items: start;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 8px;
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }

    .btn {
      border: 1px solid rgba(159, 58, 47, 0.24);
      color: var(--accent);
      text-decoration: none;
      padding: 8px 11px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: var(--accent-soft);
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 0.85rem;
    }

    .btn-flowing {
      border-color: rgba(49, 92, 124, 0.18);
      color: var(--accent-2);
      background: rgba(49, 92, 124, 0.08);
    }

    .card-body {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: minmax(320px, 420px) minmax(0, 1fr);
      min-height: 620px;
    }

    .prompt-pane {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      border-right: 1px solid var(--line);
      background:
        linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(251, 247, 240, 0.96), rgba(247, 241, 231, 0.9)),
        repeating-linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(159, 58, 47, 0.02) 0, rgba(159, 58, 47, 0.02) 28px, transparent 28px, transparent 56px);
      padding: 18px 18px 20px;
    }

    .pill {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 6px 10px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.72);
      border: 1px solid rgba(159, 58, 47, 0.12);
      color: var(--accent);
      font-size: 0.76rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 0.04em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    .pane-kicker {
      display: inline-flex;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }

    .meta-list {
      display: grid;
      gap: 10px;
      margin: 0 0 16px;
    }

    .meta-row {
      display: grid;
      gap: 2px;
    }

    .meta-row strong {
      font-size: 0.78rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    }

    .meta-row span,
    .meta-row a {
      color: var(--text);
      text-decoration: none;
      line-height: 1.45;
      word-break: break-word;
    }

    .meta-row a:hover {
      color: var(--accent);
    }

    .command-block {
      margin: 0 0 16px;
      flex: 0 0 auto;
    }

    .prompt-block {
      display: flex;
      flex: 1 1 auto;
      flex-direction: column;
      min-height: 0;
    }

    .command-block h3,
    .prompt-block h3,
    .preview-pane h3 {
      margin: 0 0 8px;
      color: var(--accent-2);
      font-size: 0.86rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    pre {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 12px 13px;
      border-radius: 14px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(49, 92, 124, 0.14);
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.82);
      color: var(--text);
      font-size: 0.84rem;
      line-height: 1.45;
      white-space: pre-wrap;
      word-break: break-word;
      font-family: "Cascadia Code", "SFMono-Regular", Consolas, monospace;
    }

    .prompt-text {
      flex: 1 1 auto;
      min-height: 0;
      overflow: auto;
      box-shadow: inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.4);
    }

    .preview-pane {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      min-height: 0;
      padding: 18px 18px 20px;
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, #fff 0%, #faf8f4 100%);
    }

    .preview-frame {
      display: flex;
      flex: 1 1 auto;
      min-height: 0;
      border: 1px solid rgba(49, 92, 124, 0.14);
      border-radius: 18px;
      overflow: hidden;
      background: #ffffff;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 24px rgba(49, 92, 124, 0.08);
    }

    iframe {
      flex: 1 1 auto;
      width: 100%;
      min-width: 0;
      height: 100%;
      border: 0;
      display: block;
      background: #fff;
    }

    @media (max-width: 980px) {
      .wrap {
        padding-left: 16px;
        padding-right: 16px;
      }

      .card-body {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }

      .prompt-pane {
        border-right: 0;
        border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
      }
    }

    @media (max-width: 900px) {
      .hero-copy {
        padding: 18px;
      }
    }

    @media (max-width: 720px) {
      .wrap {
        padding: 16px 12px 24px;
      }

      .card {
        border-radius: 14px;
      }

      .card-header {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }

      .card-header .actions {
        margin-top: 4px;
      }

      .prompt-pane,
      .preview-pane {
        padding: 14px;
      }

      .preview-frame {
        min-height: 420px;
      }

      iframe {
        min-width: 100%;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <main class="wrap">
    <section class="hero">
      <div class="hero-copy">
        <p class="eyebrow">Preview Studio</p>
        <h1>Prompt examples and style previews, shown together without tying one to the other.</h1>
        <p class="lead">Each card combines two independent ingredients: a reusable prompt template that helps a human generate newsletter markdown offline, and a visual style applied later by the preview builder to a checked-in markdown sample. The gallery is intentionally showing the combination, not claiming that the prompt owns the style.</p>
        <p class="hero-note">All markdown samples are checked in and can be replaced one by one later without changing the prompt templates.</p>
      </div>
    </section>
    <header class="section-head">
      <h2>Example Library</h2>
      <p>{{ cards|length }} prompt-driven previews</p>
    </header>
    <section class="grid">
      {% for card in cards %}
      <article class="card">
        <header class="card-header">
          <div>
            <h2>{{ card.style_name }}</h2>
            <p>{{ card.title }} · {{ card.summary }}</p>
          </div>
          <div class="actions">
            <a class="btn" href="{{ card.fixed_file }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Open Fixed (600 px)</a>
            <a class="btn btn-flowing" href="{{ card.flowing_file }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Open Flowing</a>
          </div>
        </header>
        <div class="card-body">
          <aside class="prompt-pane">
            <span class="pill pane-kicker">Prompt template</span>

            <div class="command-block">
              <h3>VS Code Slash Command</h3>
              <pre>{{ card.slash_command }}</pre>
            </div>

            <div class="prompt-block">
              <h3>Prompt Text</h3>
              <pre class="prompt-text">{{ card.prompt_body }}</pre>
            </div>
          </aside>

          <section class="preview-pane">
            <div class="preview-frame">
              <iframe src="{{ card.flowing_file }}" title="{{ card.title }} preview"></iframe>
            </div>
          </section>
        </div>
      </article>
      {% endfor %}
    </section>
  </main>
</body>
</html>
